(857, 'Duong Viet Cuong', 'cuongdv.auditor@gmail.com', '1989-03-08', 1, '0972.474542  | 0934.', '20160727123003-78177.png', 1, 'No. 47 Khuong Trung Street, Thanh Xuan, Ha Noi', 'Audit Assistant', 2, 7, 5, 5, 17, 7, 1, 1, 0, 'Position Seeking: Audit Assistant', 'NTV857', 'Knowledges\r\n- Knowledge of finance, accounting, budgeting, and cost control principles including Generally Accepted Accounting Principles. \r\n- Knowledge of automated financial and accounting reporting systems.\r\n- Knowledge of Human Resource role.\r\n- Working knowledge of short and long term budgeting and forecasting, rolling budgets, and product-line profitability analysis.\r\n\r\nHard working, ability-task, work under pressure and meet deadline\r\n\r\nTechnical skills : \r\n- Strong people leader with ability to motivate team to produce quality results in efficient manner within tight timeframes.\r\n- High energy leader experienced in leading a coperate team in fast paced, high growth.\r\n- Excellent professional written and verbal communication skill required (interested in working with both financial and other management team)\r\nBehavior skills : \r\n-Ability to multi rigorous and enterprising, capacity to work independently, good analytical and communication skills.\r\n', '20160727123003-7826.docx', 5, 0, '2016-07-27 05:30:03', '2016-08-20 13:52:49'),
