(1012, 'Doan Thu Ha ', 'hadoanthu1970@yahoo.com', '1970-03-19', 2, '84-0919408588', '20160728181310-10585.png', 4, 'E4  Phuong Mai Street, Dong Da District, Hanoi', 'GIÁM ĐỐC MARKETING', 2, 13, 1, 1, 49, 9, 1, 1, 1, 'Summary of Accomplishments\r\n*   Managed Partner relationship and PR-Marketing system\r\n*   Made plans for Business\r\n* 	Developed the channel partners based on business plans and migrate channel partners to higher levels of accreditation \r\n*   Developed channel promotional programs.\r\n* Maintained and strengthened relationships within the channel partners at all levels including sales, marketing and technical departments\r\n* Launched new products, marketing campaigns, advertising and promoted press coverage\r\n*   Developed and implemented cross marketing promotions. Surveyed customer, analyzed research and determined new features for product updates.\r\n*   Planned, directed activities of designated projects.\r\n*   Simultaneously managed multiple development projects under tight deadlines.\r\n*   Developed staffing plans, work schedules, budgets, and time lines.\r\n*   Coordinated the successful simultaneous development for many SMB projects.\r\n*   Negotiated contracts that ensured quality and met standards.\r\n*   Reviewed project reports and schedule status at each phase\r\n*   Modified time lines and work schedule accordingly.\r\n*   Prepared weekly project status reports for director.\r\n*   Have many closed relationships with the customer in many fields such as: Education, Banking, Finance, Insurance, Telecommunication, Securities, Ministries, Branches and several People’s Committee in provinces and cities\r\n   * Build up strategy PR-MKT\r\n', 'NTV1012', 'o	Good communication and interpersonal skills\r\no	Ability to problem solves and works under high pressure\r\no	Ability to work independently & teamwork\r\no	Good in written and spoken English\r\no	Good computer skills: Microsoft Word, Excel, MS Project, Corel Draw, Photoshop….\r\no	So