(2163, 'Nguyen Thi Kim Tuyen', 'kimtuyen19995@gmail.com', '1995-04-24', 2, '0948567069', NULL, 4, '1194 Lang Street, Dong Da District,Ha Noi', 'Customer services and reception; PG', 2, 3, 6, 6, 48, 1, 1, 5, 0, 'I have a strong work ethic and desire to succeed. I like to keep learning new skills\r\nwhich will benefit my company and enable me to do more in my role. I am happy to\r\ntry any new tasks and be of help in whichever way I can.', 'NTV2163', 'I am an efficient and organized person who is able to do multi-task and deal with\r\nmany different tasks at once. I have a strong background in customer services and\r\nreception and I enjoy helping people and giving them support.\r\nMy communication skills are very good and I am also confident with my English\r\nability due to the time I worked for TOPICA Group. I work well under pressure and\r\nto tight deadlines. I have a cheerful and optimistic outlook to my work and enjoy\r\nworking as part of a team as well as on my own initiative.', '20160905194039-17013.pdf', 0, 0, '2016-09-05 12:40:39', '2016-09-05 12:40:39');
